‘We have almost everything sorted out with West Ham,’ his brother and agent Rolando Zarate told Argentine radio station, Velez y su Mundo.

‘They asked him not to play against San Lorenzo but he wanted to play.

‘Mauro wanted to play because his love for Velez is very intense. But the club receive a good financial compensation.’

